cc:Work.dc:title: Vehicles - Silhouette
cc:Work.dc:description: A set of black and white images of a stylized motorcycle, car, truck, car with trailer, truck with trailer, bus and bus with trailer, similar to those shown on information signs. Each vehicle image has been separated from each other image and each image is marked as one path, to make it easy to use the specific images as imports in other svg documents.
